name: Sprott Physical Platinum and Palladium Trust
longDescription: The Trust was created to invest and hold substantially all of itsassets in physical platinum and palladium bullion. The Trust is expressly prohibited from investing in units or shares of other investment funds or collective investment schemes other than money market mutual funds and then only to the extent that its interest does not exceed 10 percentage of the total net assets of the Trust.
